      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> fish sauce</strong>,<strong> lime leaves</strong>, the juice of half your<strong> lime[s]</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and stir it all together –<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> fragrant stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
