            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> fragrant stock </strong>to the pan, give everything a good mix up and cook for 2-3 min further – this is your <strong>Thai-style broth</strong></p><p>Cut the remaining <strong>lime</strong> into wedges</p>",
