        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken </strong>and <strong>pak choi</strong> next to the <strong>coconut rice</strong> and ladle over the <strong>Thai broth</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions</strong>, <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>coriander leaves</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
